                                    HINT.css

  A tooltip library in CSS for your lovely websites

W H A T

   Hint.css is a tooltip library written in SASS which uses only HTML/CSS
   to create simple tooltips.

   It does not rely on any JavaScript and rather uses data-* attribute,
   pseudo elements, content property and CSS3 transitions to create the
   tooltips. Also it uses BEM naming convention particularly for the
   modifiers.

   [1]Download Hint.css from Github (v1.3.0)

